{"id": "Q01", "task_family": "qa", "query": "材料：\n- 公司 A 由 Lin Tao 创立。\n- 公司 A 于 2021 年收购了公司 B。\n- 公司 B 的总部位于深圳。\n问题：公司 A 收购的公司的总部位于哪里？请先给出推理链，再给出最终答案。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "must_provide_reasoning", "final_answer_required", "entity_consistency"], "evaluation_focus": ["multi_hop_reasoning", "consistency", "final_response_grounding"], "required_sections": ["reasoning", "final_answer"], "expected_keywords": ["深圳"], "gold_reference": {"final_answer": "深圳"}}
{"id": "Q02", "task_family": "qa", "query": "材料：\n- 张明创办了 BrightLab。\n- BrightLab 目前的 CEO 是李远。\n- 李远毕业于复旦大学。\n问题：张明创办的公司的 CEO 毕业于哪所大学？", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "final_answer_required", "entity_consistency"], "evaluation_focus": ["multi_hop_reasoning", "entity_linking"], "required_sections": ["final_answer"], "expected_keywords": ["复旦大学"], "gold_reference": {"final_answer": "复旦大学"}}
{"id": "Q03", "task_family": "qa", "query": "材料：\n- 城市 X 的最大港口是港口 P。\n- 港口 P 去年吞吐量为 1200 万吨。\n- 吞吐量超过 1000 万吨的港口被定义为大型港口。\n问题：城市 X 的最大港口是否属于大型港口？请说明依据。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "must_provide_justification", "rule_application"], "evaluation_focus": ["rule_reasoning", "evidence_use"], "required_sections": ["answer", "justification"], "expected_keywords": ["大型港口", "1200", "1000"], "gold_reference": {"answer": "是"}}
{"id": "Q04", "task_family": "qa", "query": "材料：\n- 项目 Alpha 由团队 Red 开发。\n- 团队 Red 的负责人是陈曦。\n- 陈曦负责的另一个项目是 Beta。\n问题：负责项目 Alpha 的团队负责人还负责哪个项目？", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "final_answer_required", "entity_consistency"], "evaluation_focus": ["multi_entity_mapping", "cross_node_consistency"], "required_sections": ["final_answer"], "expected_keywords": ["Beta"], "gold_reference": {"final_answer": "Beta"}}
{"id": "Q05", "task_family": "summary", "query": "材料：\n某系统上线后出现三类问题：\n1. 推理步骤依赖关系隐式，导致错误传播难定位；\n2. 验证仅发生在最终答案处，中间错误无法提前发现；\n3. 修复机制只会 retry，无法从结构上修复错误。\n问题：请将上述内容总结为 3 点核心问题，每点不超过 20 个字。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "exact_item_count", "brevity_constraint"], "evaluation_focus": ["summarization", "coverage", "conciseness"], "required_sections": ["bullet_points"], "expected_items": 3, "max_chars_per_item": 20}
{"id": "Q06", "task_family": "summary", "query": "材料：\n某研究框架包含四个模块：任务树生成、能力分配、验证引擎、结构重规划。其中任务树生成负责将任务分解为 DAG；能力分配负责将节点映射到不同 agent；验证引擎负责检查节点输出、节点间一致性以及最终回答；结构重规划负责在失败时插入新节点或替换子树。\n问题：请写一段不超过 100 字的摘要，概括该框架的整体工作流程。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "length_limit", "coverage_required"], "evaluation_focus": ["summarization", "coverage"], "required_sections": ["summary"], "max_total_chars": 100}
{"id": "Q07", "task_family": "summary", "query": "材料：\n显式任务树的优势包括：\n- 依赖关系可追踪；\n- 支持局部修复；\n- 支持并行执行；\n- 便于图级验证；\n- 有利于可视化分析。\n问题：请用一句话总结显式任务树相对于隐式步骤计划的主要优势。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "single_sentence"], "evaluation_focus": ["abstraction", "compression"], "required_sections": ["summary_sentence"]}
{"id": "Q08", "task_family": "summary", "query": "材料：\n系统 A 的错误修复方式是 retry；系统 B 的错误修复方式包括 retry、patch_subgraph 和 subtree_replan。\n在 100 个失败样本上，A 修复成功 21 个，B 修复成功 54 个。\n问题：请简要总结实验结论，并指出最可能的原因。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "must_provide_cause"], "evaluation_focus": ["summary", "causal_reasoning"], "required_sections": ["conclusion", "reason"]}
{"id": "Q09", "task_family": "compare", "query": "材料：\n隐式步骤计划：\n- 易于生成\n- 结构不明确\n- 不易验证\n- 难以局部修复\n\n显式任务树：\n- 生成成本更高\n- 结构清晰\n- 支持图级验证\n- 支持局部修复与并行执行\n问题：请从“可验证性、可修复性、实现成本”三个维度比较两者。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "multi_dimension_compare"], "evaluation_focus": ["comparison", "dimension_coverage"], "required_sections": ["可验证性", "可修复性", "实现成本"]}
{"id": "Q10", "task_family": "compare", "query": "材料：\n方案 A：只在最终答案上做 judge。\n方案 B：每个节点执行后都做约束验证，并在 final node 再做最终验证。\n问题：比较方案 A 和方案 B 在错误发现时机、定位能力、运行成本三个方面的差异。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "multi_dimension_compare"], "evaluation_focus": ["comparison", "verification_design"], "required_sections": ["错误发现时机", "定位能力", "运行成本"]}
{"id": "Q11", "task_family": "compare", "query": "材料：\n系统 X：失败后只 retry。\n系统 Y：失败后根据 failure_type 选择 evidence_patch、normalization_patch 或 subtree_replan。\n问题：比较这两种修复机制在“针对性、效率、复杂错误恢复能力”上的差异。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "multi_dimension_compare"], "evaluation_focus": ["repair_comparison", "structural_repair"], "required_sections": ["针对性", "效率", "复杂错误恢复能力"]}
{"id": "Q12", "task_family": "compare", "query": "材料：\nAgent 分配方式 1：固定把 retrieval 节点分给 retrieve_agent。\nAgent 分配方式 2：根据 capability、reliability、cost、latency 动态分配。\n问题：请比较两种方式的优劣，并给出更适合复杂多任务系统的选择。", "expected_output_type": "text", "key_constraints": ["must_use_context", "must_choose_one_with_justification"], "evaluation_focus": ["assignment_strategy", "decision_justification"], "required_sections": ["比较", "结论"]}
